was his brother.

01:34.628 --> 01:39.165
I understand, but we've only
gotten so much cooperation

01:39.199 --> 01:40.701
from Pakistani authorities,

01:40.734 --> 01:44.337
and I've received
no help whatsoever

01:44.370 --> 01:46.239
from our own
federal government,

01:46.272 --> 01:49.342
which prefers I back off
this altogether,

01:49.375 --> 01:51.645
and quite frankly,
our case is weak.

01:51.678 --> 01:53.647
So what you're saying is

01:53.680 --> 01:55.516
