we were at trial together.

05:43.644 --> 05:45.979
My malpractice carrier
has ordered me

05:46.012 --> 05:47.981
to advise all my clients

05:48.014 --> 05:51.585
that I have never won
a jury trial.

05:51.618 --> 05:53.453
You've still never won?

05:53.486 --> 05:56.523
I've won some bench trials,
but with a jury, I--

05:56.557 --> 05:58.892
I need to get one
under my belt, Eugene,

05:58.925 --> 06:01.528
and not just because
I love my niece,

06:01.562 --> 06:03.997
but, also, it's tough
to recruit new business

06:04.030 --> 06:06.600
