06:09.903 --> 06:13.473
I know I'm asking a lot.

06:13.507 --> 06:16.510
I need to get a "W."

06:21.915 --> 06:24.618
There is no basis in law
for these charges.

06:24.651 --> 06:27.020
A defendant can't be
an accessory-before-the-fact

06:27.053 --> 06:29.890
to a homicide that happened
in a foreign country.

06:29.923 --> 06:32.458
If there's a kidnapping
with the intent to kill,

06:32.492 --> 06:34.995
we can absolutely assert
jurisdiction here.

06:35.028 --> 06:36.429
But she wasn't kidnapped.

06:36.462 --> 06:37.864
She went to Pakistan
on vacation.

06:37.898 --> 06:40.934
He tricked her. She thought
she was going on vacation.

06:40.967 --> 06:42.936
