for his brother

06:42.969 --> 06:45.438
to have her killed
when she arrived.

06:45.471 --> 06:47.440
Are you serious?

06:47.473 --> 06:49.442
I take it you've tried
extraditing the brother.

06:49.475 --> 06:50.711
To no avail.

06:50.744 --> 06:51.978
Approach.

06:56.182 --> 06:58.719
