slightly distinguishable.

07:31.151 --> 07:34.054
-How so?
-She's the size of a cottage.

07:34.087 --> 07:36.590
-No offense.
-Offense taken.

07:36.623 --> 07:39.092
Is that how you
picked her out-- her size?

07:39.125 --> 07:41.094
No. Her face as well.

07:41.127 --> 07:43.129
In fact, I'd first
I. D.'d her face

07:43.163 --> 07:45.866
from a picture where you
couldn't even see her girth.

07:45.899 --> 07:48.869
A picture? You picked out
a mug shot before the lineup?

07:48.902 --> 07:52.506
She didn't have a mug shot.
This was her very first arrest.

07:52.539 --> 07:54.741
The D. A. showed me
just a regular picture.

07:54.775 --> 07:56.743
It wasn't a mug shot.

07:56.777 --> 07:59.112
You saw this photo
before the lineup?

07:59.145 --> 08:01.147
Look, counsel,
she's the one

08:01.181 --> 08:04.184
