the merchandise.

08:06.052 --> 08:08.021
You think you can
shake him?

08:08.054 --> 08:10.557
I'm hoping it won't
even come to that.

08:10.591 --> 08:12.058
What do you mean?

08:12.092 --> 08:14.628
Well, I think we should
bring a motion to dismiss

08:14.661 --> 08:16.930
on the basis that
the I. D. was tainted.

08:16.963 --> 08:18.031
Good idea.

08:18.064 --> 08:19.633
Yes, I thought
you'd like it.

08:22.168 --> 08:24.137
On September 14th,
I examined a body

08:24.170 --> 08:25.972
that had arrived
from Pakistan.

08:26.006 --> 08:28.141
Did you make an identification
of this body?

08:28.174 --> 08:30.143
Yes. Through dental records
I established

08:30.176 --> 08:32.212
that the body belonged
to Julie McGrath.

08:44.825 --> 08:46.326
Is this how
Julie McGrath's body

08:46.359 --> 08:48.729
arrived from Pakistan?

08:48.762 --> 08:50.564
That's correct.

08:50.597 --> 08:52.833
What did
your examination reveal?

08:52.866 --> 08:56.202
There was carbon monoxide
in her blood

08:56.236 --> 08:58.572
and soot in her lungs.

08:58.605 --> 09:00.741
Also, tests revealed
gasoline residue

09:00.774 --> 09:02.275
all over her tissue.

09:02.308 --> 09:04.745
Please, doctor,
in layman's terms.

09:04.778 --> 09:07.748
She was soaked
with gasoline,

09:07.781 --> 09:10.917
set on fire,
and then burned to death.

09:10.951 --> 09:13.754
She was burned alive?

09:13.787 --> 09:16.757
Yes.

09:18.725 --> 09:20.260
Nothing further.

09:23.897 --> 09:25.231
Mr. Donnell?

09:28.635 --> 09:31.705
No questions, your honor.

09:31.738 --> 09:32.973
Ms. Gamble?

09:33.006 --> 09:36.710
Commonwealth calls
detective Michael McGuire.

09:36.743 --> 09:38.244
We received cooperation

09:38.278 --> 09:40.714
from the Lahore Police
Department in Pakistan,

09:40.747 --> 09:42.883
and they provided us
with the details

09:42.916 --> 09:43.917
of their investigation.

09:43.950 --> 09:45.351
Detective, what did

09:45.385 --> 09:46.920
the Pakistanian
investigation reveal?

09:46.953 --> 09:48.722
That it was a homicide

09:48.755 --> 09:52.826
committed by Javed Sharif,
brother of the defendant.

09:52.859 --> 09:54.094
Was he arrested?

09:54.127 --> 09:55.228
Yes, he was.

09:55.261 --> 09:57.831
Did he make
any statements?

09:57.864 --> 09:59.966
He did. He confessed
to the killing,

10:00.000 --> 10:01.668
said it was done to protect
his brother's honor.

10:01.702 --> 10:03.303
How did setting
Julie McGrath on fire

10:03.336 --> 10:05.138
protect
the defendant's honor?

10:05.171 --> 10:07.140
Ms. McGrath
had evidently engaged

10:07.173 --> 10:09.142
in an extra-marital affair.

10:09.175 --> 10:11.144
Adultery is considered
a serious breach

10:11.177 --> 10:13.146
of a man's honor
in Pakistan.

10:13.179 --> 10:14.781
In his confession,

10:14.815 --> 10:17.884
Mr. Sharif said
he set Ms. McGrath on fire

10:17.918 --> 10:22.255
to avenge
his brother's disgrace.

10:22.288 --> 10:24.725
It was an honor killing.

10:24.758 --> 10:26.893
What do you mean,
"honor killing"?

10:26.927 --> 10:29.329
In Pakistan, there's
an ancient tribal custom.

10:29.362 --> 10:31.898
A man's honor is linked
to his possessions--

10:31.932 --> 10:35.168
gold, land, women.

10:35.201 --> 10:37.704
Detective,
was Javed Sharif

10:37.738 --> 10:40.140
ever prosecuted
for this murder?

10:40.173 --> 10:41.742
No, he was not.

10:41.775 --> 10:43.143
Why is that?

10:43.176 --> 10:45.145
According to
the Pakistani government,

10:45.178 --> 10:47.881
the defendant invoked
qisas.

10:47.914 --> 10:49.249
What does that mean?

10:49.282 --> 10:51.184
Qisas is evidently
an Islamic doctrine

10:51.217 --> 10:53.453
which is actually law
in Pakistan.

10:53.486 --> 10:56.156
It allows the heirs
of a murder victim

10:56.189 --> 10:58.024
to pardon the murderer.

10:58.058 --> 11:00.460
Mr. Sharif here
is the heir,

11:00.493 --> 11:02.929
and, in fact,
pardoned his brother.

11:02.963 --> 11:06.199
So the defendant
pardoned the man

11:06.232 --> 11:08.935
who set his wife
on fire?

11:08.969 --> 11:10.904
That's correct.

11:10.937 --> 11:13.406
Thank you, detective.

11:17.343 --> 11:19.179
