detective,

11:19.212 --> 11:21.314
what would have happened
to my client's brother

11:21.347 --> 11:24.484
had he not been pardoned?

11:24.518 --> 11:26.452
He would have faced death
by hanging.

11:26.486 --> 11:28.454
So the only way
for my client

11:28.488 --> 11:30.456
to spare the life
of his brother

11:30.490 --> 11:32.959
would be to pardon him
altogether?

11:32.993 --> 11:34.460
Yes.

11:34.494 --> 11:36.462
