is there any evidence

11:36.496 --> 11:38.298
of my client
directing his brother

11:38.331 --> 11:39.933
to commit this crime?

11:39.966 --> 11:41.334
Not to my knowledge.

11:41.367 --> 11:43.804
Is there any evidence
that my client knew

11:43.837 --> 11:45.506
this crime
was going to happen?

11:45.539 --> 11:47.508
Not to my knowledge.

11:47.541 --> 11:49.976
Thank you.

12:04.157 --> 12:06.126
You want to do
the talking?

12:06.159 --> 12:07.360
I think
it would be nice.

12:07.393 --> 12:09.262
