my best to contain him,

13:07.153 --> 13:09.556
and I think he fully
appreciates your wrath

13:09.590 --> 13:11.525
over what happened
the last time,

13:11.558 --> 13:14.394
and it should be
a very quick trial.

13:14.427 --> 13:16.396
Well, I will hold you
responsible

13:16.429 --> 13:19.265
for any antics, counsel.

13:19.299 --> 13:21.968
You're on notice.

13:23.604 --> 13:26.106
We had been seeing each other
for about three months.

13:26.139 --> 13:28.208
-Then what happened?
