13:28.241 --> 13:29.943
She wanted to work things
out with her husband.

13:29.976 --> 13:33.046
-This man?
-Yes, that's her husband.

13:33.079 --> 13:35.348
Did you ever have
any encounters with this man?

13:35.381 --> 13:37.350
