of the affair,

13:37.383 --> 13:39.252
he basically accosted me.

13:39.285 --> 13:41.221
How did he accost you, sir?

13:41.254 --> 13:43.223
I was leaving work.
He approached me

13:43.256 --> 13:45.491
in the parking lot
and threatened me.

13:45.526 --> 13:47.227
Could you describe
the threat?

13:47.260 --> 13:49.229
It was pretty vague.

13:49.262 --> 13:51.865
He just said,
"Stay away from my wife,"

13:51.898 --> 13:54.134
in what I perceive
to be a threatening tone.

13:54.167 --> 13:56.202
Did he say anything else?

13:56.236 --> 13:58.639
Yes. He said in his country,

13:58.672 --> 14:02.142
people were killed
for committing adultery.

14:04.010 --> 14:07.948
I take it when he said this,
he was very upset.

14:07.981 --> 14:10.050
-Yes.
