14:10.083 --> 14:12.418
that you had been sleeping
with his wife for three months.

14:12.452 --> 14:14.320
That's correct.

14:14.354 --> 14:16.389
This was an angry husband
blowing off steam,

14:16.422 --> 14:18.124
wasn't it, Mr. Miller?

14:18.158 --> 14:19.960
Well...

14:19.993 --> 14:21.528
Did you report him
to the police?

14:21.562 --> 14:23.496
No.

14:23.530 --> 14:26.266
So you didn't perceive
that remark to be a threat

14:26.299 --> 14:27.901
on either your life

14:27.934 --> 14:30.270
or the life
of Julie McGrath, did you?

14:30.303 --> 14:32.639
